                        <br>
                        <h4 class="bnr-para" style="text-align: left;line-height: 2em;">You may shop either as a guest (no login required) or as a logged in customer. 
                            The benefits of registering and shopping while logged in are:
                            <ul style="list-style: circle">
                                <li>Your name and payment information are saved in our secured database, so you need not enter it every time you take a course.</li>
                                <li>Check the status of your orders and track them online.</li>
                                <li>Easily re-order items you have ordered in the past</li>
                                <li>View your order history - a detailed list of each order you have placed with Shop One</li>
                                <li>Shop with just a few clicks of your mouse as your shipping and billing information is encrypted and stored in your account (which you can amend as needed)</li>
                                <li>Access product prices and special offers that unregistered customers are unable to see. </li>
                            </ul>
                            To register, click on the ‘Register for an Account’ link at the top of the page. Fill in all the mandatory fields including a valid email address, a password and then click ‘Register’. you will receive an email confirming your registration within one business day. When you return to our site, log in as a Returning Customer.</h4>

